New York based designer Nili Lotan is hosting a pop up shop in her SOHO studio space .
The pop - up boutique features a selection of Lotan 's summer essentials and a personally curated collection of local vintage finds - including jewelry , art books and wares .
If you find yourself in East Hampton this summer , head to the Orlebar Brown pop - up to find stylish swimwear , beachwear , accessories and more .
